\"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The twenty-seven creators participating across platforms will create custom content while attending the Games this summer and certain U.S. Olympic Team Trials in June.\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1548, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The twenty-seven creators\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1406}, {\"ngram\": \"platforms\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1437}, {\"ngram\": \"custom content\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1464}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1490}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1547}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertising partners can work with NBCUniversal to create sponsored posts with select creators while they are in Paris to reach the next generation of fans.\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1705, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1584, \"end\": 1596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.768311216966041e-14, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 1662, \"end\": 1667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.758176578814019e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Advertising partners\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1569}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsored posts\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1622}, {\"ngram\": \"select creators\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1643}, {\"ngram\": \"the next generation\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1696}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1704}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The full list of creators can be found below.\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1751, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The full list\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1719}, {\"ngram\": \"creators\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1731}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Paris this summer, the world's greatest athletes will compete against the backdrop of one of the most beautiful cities in the world where the modern Olympic Games were conceived 130 years ago.\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1756, \"end\": 1761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.758176578814019e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world's greatest athletes\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1804}, {\"ngram\": \"the backdrop\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1838}, {\"ngram\": \"the most beautiful cities\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1874}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 1887}, {\"ngram\": \"the modern Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will be the third time Paris has hosted the Olympics (1900 and 1924), tying London for the most as a Summer Games host.\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 2073, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1977, \"end\": 1982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.758176578814019e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2030, \"end\": 2036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.99999990553943, \"rank\": 8.712912565272924e-08, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the third time\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1976}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2006}, {\"ngram\": \"a Summer Games host\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2072}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Los Angeles (1932, 1984) will tie those two cities when it hosts the first Summer Games in the U.S. in 32 years in 2028.\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2074, \"end\": 2085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.30704162709642e-14, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those two cities\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2124}, {\"ngram\": \"the first Summer Games\", \"from\": 2139, \"to\": 2161}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2173}, {\"ngram\": \"32 years\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2185}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The organizers of Paris 2024 are reimagining the Games to make them more accessible to the public and to showcase their city to the world.\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2334, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The organizers\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2210}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2219}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2250}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2293}, {\"ngram\": \"their city\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2320}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2324, \"to\": 2333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a first, competitions will be held amidst iconic Parisian landmarks - beach volleyball at the Eiffel Tower, equestrian at the Palace of Versailles, and urban sports at Place de la Concorde.\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2506, \"end\": 2526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.3014826903183307e-12, \"text\": \"Place de la Concorde\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2359}